        "text_lat": "Vox clara ecce รญntonat,^lobscรบra quรฆque รญncrepat:^lprocul fugรฉntur sรณmnia;^lab รฆthre Christus prรณmicat.^pMens iam resรบrgat tรณrpida^lquรฆ sorde exstat sรกucia;^lsidus refรบlget iam novum,^lut tollat omne nรณxium.^pE sursum Agnus mรญttitur^llaxรกre gratis dรฉbitum;^lomnes pro indulgรฉntia^lvocem demus cum lรกcrimis,^pSecรบndo ut cum fรบlserit^lmundรบmque horror cรญnxerit,^lnon pro reรกtu pรบniat,^lsed nos pius tunc prรณtegat.^pSummo Parรฉnti glรณria^lNatรณque sit victรณria,^let Flรกmini laus dรฉbita^lper sรฆculรณrum sวฝcula."
