        "text_lat": "Marรญa, quรฆ mortรกlium^lpreces amรกnter รฉxcipis,^lrogรกmus ecce sรบpplices,^lnobis adรฉsto pรฉrpetim.^pAdรฉsto, si nos crรญminum^lcatรฉna stringit hรณrrida;^lcito resรณlve cรณmpedes^lquรฆ corda culpis รญlligant.^pSuccรบrre, si nos sวฝculi^lfallax imรกgo pรฉllicit,^lne mens salรบtis trรกmitem,^loblรญta cรฆli, dรฉserat.^pSuccรบrre, si vel cรณrpori^ladvรฉrsa sors impรฉndeat;^lfac sint quiรฉta tรฉmpora,^lรฆtรฉrnitas dum lรบceat.^pTuis et esto fรญliis^ltutรฉla mortis tรฉmpore,^lut, te iuvรกnte, cรณnsequi^lperรฉnne detur prวฝmium.^pPatri sit et Parรกclito^ltuรณque Nato glรณria,^lqui veste te mirรกbili^lcircumdedรฉrunt grรกtiรฆ. Amen."
