        "text_lat": "Quem terra, pontus, วฝthera^lcolunt, adรณrant, prวฝdicant^ltrinam regรฉntem mรกchinam,^lclaustrum Marรญรฆ bรกiulat.^pCui luna, sol et รณmnia^ldesรฉrviunt per tรฉmpora,^lperfรบsa cรฆli grรกtia^lgestant puรฉllรฆ vรญscera.^pBeรกta mater mรบnere,^lcuius, supรฉrnus รกrtifex,^lmundum pugรญllo cรณntinens,^lventris sub arca clausus est.^pBeรกta cรฆli nรบntio,^lfecรบnda Sancto Spรญritu,^ldesiderรกtus gรฉntibus^lcuius per alvum fusus est.^pIesu, tibi sit glรณria,^lqui natus es de Vรญrgine,^lcum Patr>e et almo Spรญritu,^lin sempitรฉrna sวฝcula.Amen."
