        "text_lat": "Tristes erant Apรณstoli^lde nece sui Dรณmini,^lquem morte crudelรญssima^lsรฆvi damnรกrant รญmpii.^pSermรณne blando Angelus^lprรฆdรญxit muliรฉribus:^lยซIn Galilวฝa Dรณminus^lvidรฉndus est quantรณciusยป.^pIllรฆ dum pergunt cรณncitรฆ^lApรณstolis hoc dรญcere,^lvidรฉntes eum vรญvere,^lรณsculant pedes Dรณmini.^pQuo รกgnito, discรญpuli^lin Galilวฝa prรณpere^lpergunt vidรฉre fรกciem^ldesiderรกtam Dรณmini.^pEsto perรฉnne mรฉntibus^lpaschรกle, Iesu, gรกudium,^let nos renรกtos grรกtiรฆ^ltuis triรบmphis รกggrega.^pSit, Christe, tibi glรณria,^lqui regno mortis รณbruto,^lpandรญsti per Apรณstolos^lvitรฆ lucรญsque sรฉmitas. Amen."
